1
00:00:22,880 --> 00:00:24,080
Zixi.

2
00:00:24,440 --> 00:00:27,040
Since you bought me time for the exam last time,

3
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:28,880
I was very moved.

4
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:31,570
I felt that you were full of a sense of justice.

5
00:00:32,280 --> 00:00:34,240
I really appreciated you.

6
00:00:36,080 --> 00:00:38,080
Ever since I met you that time...

7
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:42,880
Excuse me, this seat is taken.

8
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:44,720
Donghai 183.

9
00:00:45,360 --> 00:00:46,760
Who are you?

10
00:00:47,080 --> 00:00:48,960
Yin Zixi won't come.

11
00:00:53,760 --> 00:00:54,720
What do you mean?

12
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:55,480
I'm here

13
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:58,340
to return the 230,000 you tipped in the livestream.

14
00:00:59,440 --> 00:01:00,880
I spent the money.

15
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:03,000
I can spend it however I want.

16
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,680
If she wants to return it,

17
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:07,680
let Yin Zixi do it herself.

18
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:09,640
If you want to impress her with money,

19
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:11,560
I advise you to give up now.

20
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:14,560
Who are you?

21
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:17,020
What does this have to do with you?

22
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,800
I'm her

23
00:01:19,520 --> 00:01:20,840
manager.

24
00:01:21,320 --> 00:01:22,080
Oh.

25
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,720
So you are Senior An.

26
00:01:25,080 --> 00:01:26,760
Zixi mentioned you to me.

27
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:29,200
I thought you were a good guy then.

28
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,640
Looking at it now,

29
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:33,720
you are quite an incompetent manager.

30
00:01:34,240 --> 00:01:35,440
I'll give your words back to you:

31
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:38,280
Who are you and what does this have to do with you?

32
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,080
Does Zixi know

33
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,610
that you're doing this?

34
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,320
Do you think Zixi would be reluctant to part with this money?

35
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:45,960
I'm just worried

36
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:48,360
that someone acting on their own

37
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:50,680
might betray Zixi's trust.

38
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,520
Speaking from experience,

39
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:55,850
I advise you to worry more about yourself.

40
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:57,120
No matter how much money you have,

41
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:58,640
it belongs to your parents.

42
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,640
Without them,

43
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:01,600
you are nothing.

44
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:04,920
Senior,

45
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,760
you don't have any

46
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:10,289
other intentions toward Zixi, do you?

47
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,720
That's my business.

48
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,720
It has nothing to do with you.

49
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,600
to prevent this from happening.

50
00:02:21,079 --> 00:02:24,000
I hereby apply

51
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:27,520
to disable the tip function.

52
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,760
Why disable it?

53
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:32,040
If I were a partner,

54
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:33,240
I would not agree.

55
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,640
That's why we didn't partner up.

56
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,840
Are you provoking me?

57
00:02:38,079 --> 00:02:39,040
No.

58
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,800
I want to grow the business

59
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,560
before recruiting my bestie.

60
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,400
Hello, Mom.

61
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:45,960
Ah.

62
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,020
I'm coming out now.

63
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:49,240
Go ahead.

64
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:57,440
How should I write this?

65
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:03,320
Senior, I've decided.

66
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:05,640
From today on, I will turn off the tipping feature

67
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:07,840
and only do e-commerce live streaming.

68
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:08,800
Okay.

69
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,520
You don't object?

70
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,560
I don't.

71
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,600
I didn't expect you to agree so readily.

72
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:18,360
I spent the whole night thinking about how to bring it up.

73
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:20,680
Is it set up here?

74
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:23,440
Hey.

75
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,440
Donghai 183.

76
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,440
Wait a minute.

77
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:29,400
What's with this message?

78
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:35,160
Donghai 183 is Liang Chen.

79
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,079
You guessed right.

80
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,760
Have you met him?

81
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:39,920
Yes.

82
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:41,920
The money was also returned.

83
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:44,040
Oh.

84
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,120
Alright.

85
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:50,280
It's time to plan tonight's live stream.

86
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:53,040
The manufacturer just brought over some new clothes.

87
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:54,370
I picked out a few items.

88
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,200
We should start with the product introduction tonight.

89
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:58,840
Senior, why didn't you tell me?

90
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:03,480
Why didn't you tell me you were meeting Liang Chen?

91
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:05,650
Is it because it wasn't necessary?

92
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:09,380
Wouldn't it be more appropriate for me to reject his gifts?

93
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:11,490
Or is it because you don't trust me?

94
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:14,200
You don't believe I would actually reject him?

95
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:19,060
Let's prepare for tonight's livestream first.

96
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,160
Yang Qian.

97
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,520
Let's rest here for a bit.

98
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:19,960
Why did you bring so many clothes?

99
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:21,480
It was my mom.

100
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,720
Look.

101
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,680
What is this?

102
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:27,240
These are my mom's live streaming notes.

103
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,720
She saw your live stream get popular

104
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:31,400
and wants me to learn how to do it from you.

105
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:32,360
Oh.

106
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,159
Really?

107
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:35,720
Ah.

108
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:37,159
Tell me,

109
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:40,690
what should I pay attention to when I first start streaming?

110
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,240
Nothing much.

111
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:43,720
The most important thing

112
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,840
is to grind hard.

113
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:45,960
Ah.

114
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:49,159
Yin Zixi, prepare to stream.

115
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:51,720
Hello.

116
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,400
Ready.

117
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:56,600
Yin Zixi, start the dance segment.

118
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,920
Let's go.

119
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:02,440
Yin Zixi, there's a match tonight.

120
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,720
All troops, attack.

121
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,360
That's enough.

122
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:09,680
You're almost turning into a robot.

123
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:15,080
It's really nothing.

124
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,960
What job isn't hard work?

125
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,240
Sigh.

126
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,280
I finally made it to college,

127
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:22,600
I still want to enjoy

128
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:24,130
my wonderful college life.

129
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:27,280
Yeah.

130
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:29,640
What's wrong?

131
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:30,960
Do you regret it?

132
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:35,000
Maybe.

133
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:42,560
Lately, I often sit in the same spot

134
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,120
watching the sunrise and sunset,

135
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:46,480
watching the person in front of me constantly grow and change.

136
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,560
Who is this person?

137
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:49,680
She made me restart

138
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,360
my campus life.

139
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:54,960
This song was inspired by her,

140
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:57,440
and that's how I started writing it.

141
00:06:58,760 --> 00:06:59,640
Here,

142
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:02,800
I want to say to the person who has been by my side,

143
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,640
I'm sorry.

144
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:12,560
Waiting to say good morning just as it gets dark.

145
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:17,720
Just finished breakfast and evening is here.

146
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:21,840
By your side day and night.

147
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:26,360
Wanting to accompany you every minute.

148
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:30,800
The road never goes dark after nightfall.

149
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:36,560
Footsteps and silhouettes all fall into your chest.

150
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:39,800
Turning a few corners.

151
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,320
The red light is on.

152
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,840
Isn't this An Yufan's voice?

153
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:46,300
Why isn't he going back to the Student Union?

154
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,440
Is it that good?

155
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,420
If you want to listen, go outside.

156
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,760
Huiying, you continue.

157
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:53,760
Okay, President.

158
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:54,800
The person who stole the exam paper

159
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,520
has already turned themselves in to the school.

160
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:58,880
The students who cheated also received severe criticism.

161
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,440
According to the cheating students,

162
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:03,900
the whistleblower should be Yin Zixi from Journalism Class 1.

163
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:09,280
Yes, tipping is turned off.

164
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:11,120
I will start livestreaming sales from now on.

165
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:13,240
Babies, you must support me.

166
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:16,640
Oh, this one.

167
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,440
This is also from the manufacturer.

168
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:20,840
The material is very soft and not scratchy.

169
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,720
Just be careful when washing it.

170
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:24,120
They also have other styles.

171
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:26,000
Let me get them to show you.

172
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:31,760
Auntie, these styles need to be restocked.

173
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,240
They sell so well.

174
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:36,720
I'll have them pack the new arrivals and send them to you.

175
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:37,559
Thank you, Auntie.

176
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:37,960
Okay.

177
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,200
Brother.

178
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:51,600
The women's clothes you bought,

179
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:52,880
we can't even wear them.

180
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:54,200
Give them to your classmates.

181
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:57,160
I've already given them to the entire girls' dorm.

182
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:59,160
Now everyone looks at me strangely.

183
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:02,280
Are they looking at you with admiration?

184
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,360
Admiration?

185
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:07,000
The way they look at me now

186
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,860
makes me feel like a huge pervert.

187
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:11,880
Hold that pervert thought.

188
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:13,280
Come look at this.

189
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:21,880
Brother, I spoke out of turn before.

190
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:24,240
Can you let me go?

191
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:27,640
Impossible.

192
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:19,160
Don't miss out.

193
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,760
Here, classmate.

194
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:24,200
Hey, classmate, please support us.

195
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:27,580
What are you doing?

196
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,040
Wen Lingli.

197
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:32,520
Yin Zixi.

198
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,320
Did Liang Chen make you do this?

199
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,240
No, no, no.

200
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:36,800
I picked it up.

201
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,240
Just helping hand it out.

202
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:39,880
This woman.

203
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:41,560
I won't let her get away with this.

204
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:43,760
You should watch your step too.

205
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:52,200
Did you pull an all-nighter?

206
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,360
Assistant Casting Director: Xi Chongjing

207
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:43,280
Props Assistant: Li Kunxiao

208
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:45,200
Grip Truck: Yi Mingle

209
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:47,160
Yi Tong
